show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/PPrX6w
show.description: A humble Mumbai groundskeeper, Sourav, secretly wields the legendary Phantom Shot, a mythical cricket strike that defies physics. When his hidden talent is discovered, greed, rivalry, and power-hungry ambition ignite around him. Betrayal, stolen magic, and a fallen hero’s rise culminate as Sourav proves that divinity lies not in a bat, but in the man who holds it. Ultimately, the true Cricket Champion reclaims his destiny with quiet, unstoppable grace. Watch now.
